        <updateDate>2017-01-12T15:20:22Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>West Coast Ocean Protection Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Outer Continental Shelf Lands Act to prohibit the Bureau of Ocean Energy Management from issuing a lease for the exploration, development, or production of oil or natural gas in any area of the outer Continental Shelf off the coast of California, Oregon, or Washington.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
